node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Georgios Tataridis | Interiors on June 21, 2021. May be an image of furniture and living room.

node.text:
It's my pleasure working on your project Tom and Susanne (we are still working on it).

The location of the house it's in Germany near to Köln.

Things that were requested:
A many-sided sofa, the kitchen should look like a bar and to use that type of fireplace which is already ordered.

The wine cozy corner asked to be highlited
and I added leather on walls and led strips.

The green color and gold touches make the interior design more colorful.

Overall, the end result is very close to what
I imagined in the beginning.

Let me know your opinion.
